title: Don Carlos
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Italian, Fast food, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This cafeteria has vegan breakfast and lunch. For breakfast croissants and cookies, fruit salads, fruit juices, and dairy-free milk. For lunch there is a selection of vegan staples such as pasta and grains, seitan and tofu dishes.
